    %section#bar-charts
      %h1 Bar & Column Charts

      %p
        For bar charts, add the class <code>render-to-bar-chart</code> to an existing
        <code>&lt;table&gt;</code> element. By default, the first column of the table will be used
        for bar labels, and each remaining column will be rendered as a group of bars.

      %p
        Add the <code>render-to-column-chart</code> class for a column chart instead of a bar chart.

