    %section#pie-charts
      %h1 Pie Charts

      %p
        Rendering a pie chart is as simple as adding the class <code>render-to-pie-chart</code> to
        an existing <code>&lt;table&gt;</code> element. By default, the first column of the table
        will be used to name the slices of the pie, and the values in the last column will be used
        to determine the width of each slice.

